transcript.text: Hello, welcome to Onpenshop.
Here in this video we are going to understand promotional or pop up message feature.
So what is promotional or pop up message?
It's something when a customer comes to your website, it will pops up and show some message.
It may be a for a specific product, for a specific discount, OK.
It is helpful for your marketing purpose if you want to promote any specific product, OK, Also you can keep some coupon code into it.
So what is actual promotional message?
So we will just show you if you open the front store.
So it will be popped up like this.
Now how can you set this message or this screen?
Just go to the admin, go to the store configuration site setting put promotional in search bar South.
You will see enable disable promotional message section.
Just make it yes and save it.
Once you will save it, go to the store personalization here you will see promotional content message open it.
So here this one we have already created.
So I am just action edit or you can add it by clicking on add button available to retailer.
So it will be only available for retailer customer display both before logging and after logging.
So both means whenever customer is logged in or he is not logged in it will be displayed then pages to be displayed for.
So on which page you want to show it.
If you want to show it only contained page just select the contained page.
If you want to show it on some static page, select the static page.
If you want to show on product page particular product page then depending on your requirement you can show it.
For now we are shaving it on all pages then promotional patterns.
So it is not only for from pop up message.
There are total 4 patterns which we are giving you.
So I just show you.
So here the promotional message a pop up message which I have shown you already.
Then there is a another option that's called slider which will be come into the bottom right corner.
Then the toggle option which will be visible in the left hand side and top header which will be visible at top header part.
Then a height this height and width of the box which you want to show let's say if you are going with the proper message.
So this height that is the height and width of this box if you are showing in slider then the box size.
So you need to manage box size over here.
So right now we have uploaded a image of 42640 pixels.
So we have just kept that then time would be one minute and delay time would be one second.
And here title you can give discount for mug or anything.
Then here you can put any text you can upload a image.
So whatever you want to do if you want to upload image here just select the image section go to the upload button choose your file click on send it to server click on OK.
So the file will be look like this your image then promotional message duration.

So if you want to set it for any specific duration like this message should be visible from this date to this date that you can set it over here like here is A to date and from date then status would be activate and click on save button.
So it will be visible like this.
That's it.
So in this way you can set promotional message or a pop up message.
Thank you.
If you have any more concerns, please contact us at support at the rate on printshop.com.
